{"tid":1708702,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"係連登問點溝仔係咪好on9","createTime":"2019-11-11T16:08:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-12T00:46:27.000Z","uid":106944,"like":6,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"26468dfb87470574aac27161e1b45f791e3379a3","tid":1708702,"uid":106944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T16:08:09.000Z","msg":"最近對個groupmate有咗好感 <br />\n有時有啲gag剩係得我get佢/佢get我 成日兩個講完痴線嘢但側邊groupmate發現唔到就兩個互望忍笑<br />\n但其實present都完埋 已經再冇同佢一齊做project嘅藉口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n平時上堂佢會同佢自己班fd坐 我連點開始每日傾計呢啲野都唔識...簡單啲嚟講我係無從入手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就快final又就快完sem 我可能冇乜機會再同佢接觸了 <br />\n啊啊啊啊啊啊啊(;&acute;༎ຶД༎ຶ<code>)\n星期五成班groupmate一齊係旺角食完飯 諗住返屋企個陣 因為有手足開始set rb同埋有狗\n佢就問我洗唔洗送我去搭車 我話下咁好？ 佢話下一陣你比狗打咁點算 嗚啊(;&acute;༎ຶД༎ຶ</code>)咁樣得唔得㗎我唔想自作多情呀<br />\n點算好 集思廣益 我唔想柒 但我連第一步都唔識行<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n對唔住 港難當前我仲諗兒女私情<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e53065200389dd04db8fa28983a5c9165832f8d","tid":1708702,"uid":106944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T16:08:59.000Z","msg":"利申 絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4003631d66a1bbf2502d1116c547c5a9be4b925","tid":1708702,"uid":233705,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T16:21:59.000Z","msg":"gay<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1f5f3886588634b234cdaed519b890590ea9b4c","tid":1708702,"uid":208285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T16:22:29.000Z","msg":"雙方咩樣"},{"pid":"66c2d1b6ba3bd510412b5fe0670a98aed3d13ba1","tid":1708702,"uid":154109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T16:23:38.000Z","msg":"扮有嘢唔識 whatsapp問佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6563974e6f8b2c2910966058ce08f835b3a722b","tid":1708702,"